TY  - JOUR
TI  - The Optimality of Boiteux-Ramsey Pricing
AU  - Dierker, Egbert
AB  - [Consider an economy with one public enterprise that is subject to a budgetary constraint and charges prices according to the first order necessary conditions suggested by Boiteux (1956) or, in another context, by Ramsey (1927). We state (restrictive) conditions sufficient to ensure that the resulting allocation is second best.]
